title: Mark Kelly Wins Arizona Senate Race, Putting Democrats a Seat From Control
description: Mr. Kelly, who ran as a bipartisan legislator devoted to the needs of Arizona, defeated Blake Masters, a Republican newcomer whose ideological fervor failed to win over enough independent voters.
dc:creator: Jazmine Ulloa
media:credit: Caitlin O'Hara for The New York Times
media:description: Senator Mark Kelly of Arizona celebrated his re-election with his wife, former Representative Gabby Giffords, at Barrio Cafe in Phoenix on Saturday.
